cp|8|AT|^B@2^Z@3^*Bhondo717 ^*N|cp||at|First of all let me explain my 1S bid. There were a lot of private chats going on, and I simply miscounted my points. I have a clear pass. However, because I did open, I caused them to miss game but that was not my intent. Further, 3C was a forcing bid, and Ginny should not pass. They can make 3N. So, Ginny needs to find a bid over 3C.|
